DISCLAIMER:

This software is designed to permanently delete files using the German VSITR 
algorithm. Files deleted with this software CANNOT be recovered. Use at your 
own risk. The authors are not responsible for any data loss or damage caused 
by the use of this software.

This software is intended for educational purposes and legitimate data 
sanitization needs only. Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with 
all applicable laws and regulations regarding data destruction.